The first video off of their forthcoming LP #AfrikanSauce - a continuation of the #LiveandDieinAfrika theme - Kenyan group Sauti Sol released Melanin, on Monday. The LP will feature the biggest names in African music and the Kenyan group will be making a release monthly for the next 12 months. Melanin was written & performed by Sauti Sol & Patoranking, co-written by Nviiri Sande, and was directed by Clarence Peters. Check out the video Koroga Festival See Sauti Sol live this weekend at the 20th edition of Koroga Festival! Featuring Heavy K and Freshlyground, donâ€™t miss the biggest Koroga Festival yet! You can get tickets here.